sentences: He produced the Klaxons album Myths of the Near Future in 2007 which won the Mercury Prize.
In 2008, he formed the Last Shadow Puppets with Miles Kane and Alex Turner, as both drummer and producer.
Their second album, Everything You've Come to Expect, was released in 2016.
Ford produced and played keys on Arctic Monkeys' fifth album, AM, released in 2013.

Ford has produced the 14th Depeche Mode album Spirit released on 17 March 2017, as well as the fourth studio album of the UK band Everything Everything under the title A Fever Dream, released on 18 August 2017.
